description:
Add WebSocket connection to tick-board for real-time updates:

Implementation in tick-board.ts:
private ws: WebSocket | null = null;

private connectWebSocket() {
  const protocol = location.protocol === 'https:' ? 'wss:' : 'ws:';
  this.ws = new WebSocket(`${protocol}//${location.host}/ws`);
  this.ws.onmessage = (event) => this.handleRealtimeUpdate(JSON.parse(event.data));
  this.ws.onclose = () => setTimeout(() => this.connectWebSocket(), 1000);
}

Handle message types:
- tick_created: add to ticks array
- tick_updated: update tick in array
- tick_deleted: remove from array

Test: Open board in two tabs, update tick in one, verify other updates
